data.description: Country living in this small rural subdivision.  This charming 4 bedrooms, 3 baths home is a and ideal rural retreat. Enjoy your morning coffee with the sunrise on the back deck  and the beautiful sunsets on the front porch.  This home has a lot to offer.  Walk into the open living room with hardwood floors and fireplace to gather around for cozy evenings... The eat in kitchen is bright and inviting with stainless appliances, hardwood floors, breakfast bar, and eating area with sliding door to the deck.     Master bedroom with ensuite and walk in closet.   Two  additional bedrooms and full bath on main floor.    Downstairs is the 4th bedroom, a 3rd bath with shower, Family room and wet bar,  which makes this the perfect place for entertaining.  Main floor laundry off the kitchen. 3 car garage. Perfect for vehicles and extra storage needs.  Back deck: Step outside to enjoy the scenic views of your 1.11-acre lot.  Features include: Hardwood floors, gas fireplace, egress window in basement, heated 3 car garage.  Freezer in basement stays.  Updates:  Stainless kitchen appliances 2020, New Roof 2022, All New Triple pane Windows with lifetime warranty through Window World and back Patio Door 2021. New Furnace and Air Conditioner 2021, New Water Heater 2021. House is being sold AS-IS.
